title: Sawbones: Why Doctors Don't Fix Teeth
description:
We've joked a lot about how Dr. Sydnee doesn't know much about teeth, but this week we're explaining exactly why. It all goes back ... to The Historic Rebuff.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
